hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/3805477/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%99%82%E9%9A%94%E8%BF%914%E5%B9%B4+%E5%B0%87%E5%86%8D%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96"}]}